      <!-- Ryan's Instant Porridge Recipe -->
      <div class="recipe-card">
        <h3>Ryan's Instant Porridge Recipe</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Add 4 tablespoons of flour to a cup or bowl.</li>
          <li>Slowly add cold water (less than half a cup) and stir well to form a smooth paste (ensure no lumps remain).</li>
          <li>Gradually pour in hot water (or hot milk) while stirring until you reach your desired thickness.</li>
          <li>Add your favorite sweetener or flavor.</li>
          <li>Your porridge is ready to enjoy!</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Ryan's High Fibre Porridge Recipe -->
      <div class="recipe-card">
        <h3>Ryan's High Fibre Porridge Recipe (2 servings)</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Mix 4 tablespoons of Ryan’s porridge flour with 1 cup of cold water to form a paste.</li>
          <li>Boil 2 cups of water or milk.</li>
          <li>Add the paste while stirring on low heat.</li>
          <li>Cook for 7–10 minutes, stirring occasionally.</li>
          <li>Sweeten to taste and serve hot.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Flavour Recipes -->
