        <h3>Flavour Variations</h3>
        <p>Enhance your porridge experience with these creative flavour recipes:</p>
        
        <h4>Lemorific (Lemon Twist)</h4>
        <ol>
          <li>Prepare your porridge as per the base recipe.</li>
          <li>Add 1 teaspoon of lemon zest and 1 tablespoon of fresh lemon juice.</li>
          <li>Mix in a drizzle of honey for extra sweetness.</li>
          <li>Garnish with a few mint leaves and serve warm.</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h4>Coconutrific (Creamy Coconut)</h4>
        <ol>
          <li>Prepare your porridge as usual.</li>
          <li>Stir in 1/4 cup of coconut milk and 2 tablespoons of shredded coconut.</li>
          <li>Add a dash of vanilla extract and a pinch of salt.</li>
          <li>Top with toasted coconut flakes for crunch.</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h4>Banarific (Banana Bliss)</h4>
        <ol>
          <li>Mash one ripe banana and mix into your prepared porridge.</li>
          <li>Add a pinch of cinnamon and a drizzle of maple syrup or honey.</li>
          <li>Top with banana slices and a sprinkle of chopped walnuts.</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h4>Chocorific (Cocoa Delight)</h4>
        <ol>
          <li>Prepare your base porridge recipe.</li>
          <li>Mix in 1 tablespoon of cocoa powder and a handful of chocolate chips.</li>
          <li>Add a small pinch of salt to balance the cocoa flavour.</li>
          <li>Stir well and serve with a dollop of whipped cream if desired.</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h4>Nutrific (Nutty Boost)</h4>
        <ol>
          <li>Prepare your porridge as the base recipe.</li>
          <li>Fold in a mixture of chopped nuts (almonds, walnuts) and seeds (chia, flaxseed) – about 2 tablespoons each.</li>
          <li>Add a handful of dried fruits (raisins or cranberries) for extra texture.</li>
          <li>Mix thoroughly and enjoy a nutritious twist!</li>
        </ol>
        
